Some of the very old and famous nonveg hotels are in surrounding.

featured_reviews.review_id:
First of all I want to inform you about jumah timing i.e. 01:45 kutbah.
Mosque is located in the middle of village kalakhel gird kaimganj. A lot of space for parking cars or bikes near by the mosque. Behind  the mosque, there is a pond and a date tree that gives nice appearance to mosque from behind. Capacity of mosque near about 300 people may be offer namaz under roof and more than 300 people uncovered area at same time. Water is always available for wuzu. Thank you
